{"tid":1453673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（超突發！）又爆多單銀行內幕比大家知！","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:56:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:41:59.000Z","uid":11148,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ff799bff640fcdc98ea31163ed1793cc2037d2e8","tid":1453673,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:56:31.000Z","msg":"轉貼 <br />\n（超突發！）又爆多單銀行內幕比大家知！！！最新消息！！！<br />\n<br />\n今朝有位ibanker死黨wtsapp我！佢班老闆客（幾廿億身家果d），今朝已經開始全數將資產換成美金（有部分是換成歐羅）！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n然後，狠人岩岩問左幾個做Hedge Fund的朋友，佢地話好多基金佬今朝都開始沾空港幣！佢地都異口同聲咁建議大家：可以的話！香港人都快手去換呀！<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今次連港府都未必keep到聯繫匯率！（其實幾個月前已經有好多行家吹風，話港幣就玩完！）</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5月中，行內一個好出名的對沖基金大鱷Kyle Bass一早高調唱淡港元，質疑香港的外匯儲備不足以支撑聯繫匯率制度，聲言公司正主力沽空港元。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢當時係咁講：參考國際貨幣基金組織（IMF）的標準，香港外匯儲備最少須達4,950億元（美元‧下同），遠高於目前的4,360億元。他又質疑，在金管局報稱的外匯儲備中，僅得570億元（約13%）可供使用，形容香港的外匯儲備「匱乏得可憐」。他預料，港元聯繫匯率將於2047年自動失效，問題只是市場何時開始將此因素納入考慮，並建議投資者盡早將手上港元轉成美元。（狠人check過7月最新的數字，現在比5月的儲備更低！）<br />\n<br />\n再加上近日發生的事，大家還相信港幣嗎？以下圖片是一班金融業同路人發起的816全城曬錢日之文宣圖，狠人幫手轉發！（無論是概念和方法，狠人也深表認同！）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dbr4zxN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDbr4zxN.jpg&h=a5c12091&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f310Sjs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff310Sjs.jpg&h=854560d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ODe53q8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FODe53q8.jpg&h=e45f56c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zTNvu58.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzTNvu58.jpg&h=49feff36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/754xJq9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F754xJq9.jpg&h=26ffb2f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GZjUWL9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGZjUWL9.jpg&h=707f68c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HTJOgMa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHTJOgMa.jpg&h=712ee93c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FFinanceFellow%2F&d=bh6oHdTJShmr8W3AdcicpCPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=009d31ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/FinanceFellow/</a><br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算得一萬幾千都要拎出黎揸cash <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c58876f749aa7667f0ab6dbe8c688054337dcb","tid":1453673,"uid":171718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:59:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a41897012148bf900873d8a57c7ccf2efb05dce6","tid":1453673,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1008fa9d24c8bca5b1cbc90137326179c8571abb","tid":1453673,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:59:59.000Z","msg":"高汁幫推"},{"pid":"6906c6e50777ab142dd8213d1157e10751631a59","tid":1453673,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9